contentrichtext.text: '''Oyster Bay''' may refer to: == Place names == ;In Australia * [[Oyster Bay, New South Wales]], a suburb of Sydney, Australia * [[Great Oyster Bay]], a bay on the east coast of Tasmania, Australia ;In South Africa * [[Oyster Bay, Eastern Cape]], South Africa, a small coastal hamlet and resort located about 14km west of St Francis Bay on the Eastern Cape Coast ;In Tanzania * [[Oyster Bay, Tanzania]], a popular resort town and suburb of Dar es Salaam, Tanzania ;In the United States * [[Oyster Bay (town), New York]], a town in Nassau County on Long Island, New York **[[Oyster Bay Cove]], a town within the town of Oyster Bay on Long Island ** [[Oyster Bay (hamlet), New York]], a hamlet on the north shore of Long Island, in the Town of Oyster Bay, New York *** [[Oyster Bay (inlet), New York]], also '''Oyster Bay Harbor''', an inlet on the north shore of Long Island, New York ** [[South Oyster Bay]], a lagoon off the southern shore of Long Island, New York * [[Massapequa, New York]], which was called ''South Oyster Bay'' until late in the 19th century * [[Oyster Bay, Washington]], a small bay in [[Totten Inlet]], at the south end of Puget Sound in Washington * [[Oyster Bay, Florida]], a bay in Lee County, Florida == Ships == *[[USS Oyster Bay (AGP-6)|USS ''Oyster Bay'' (AGP-6)]], a United States Navy ship in commission as a motor torpedo boat tender (AGP-6) from 1943 to 1946 and out of commission in reserve as a seaplane tender (AVP-28) from 1949 to 1957 * {{intitle}} * {{lookfrom}} {{disambig}}
